<h2>svir.no</h2>
      <p>Prototype of an AI-powered urine test app for detecting UTI at home
        <h6>Role in the project</h6>
        <p>Product discovery and prototype testing as the projectsâ€™ sole researcher/designer</p>
      <h6>Methods</h6>
      <p><span>Experience mapping:</span> both assumption-based and post-research;
        <br>
        <span>Customer interviews:</span> interviewing potential customers to understand their UTI stories and discover
        opportunities;
        <br>
        <span>Facilitation:</span> Workshop to explicit and align the objectives of the team (using exercises from
        Google Ventures Brand Sprint);
        <br>
        <span>Prototyping:</span> and testing the experience of taking the test - using a physical card and a smartphone
        app;
      </p>
      </p>
